InfoItems.Info: Converted GDTF to grandMA2 fixture type with Share Converter version 1.4.1
New fixture type based on Robin iPainte LTM WB from Robe Lighting

Don’t be fooled by its size, the diminutive iPAINTE® LTM punches way above its size and weight. This little powerhouse will never fail to amaze with its power, precision and effects display. Taking up little space on your truss, its capable of making big statements! With 170mm front lens, exceptional optical quality together with a comprehensive feature set, this 30 kg kg fixture maximizes WashBeam flexibility and performance from its compact frame. The innovative optical design offers remarkable versatility. With its 170mm front lens and 2:1 field ratio, the iPAINTE® LTM enhances optical flexibility with a zoom range of 3°- 52°, narrowing the iris allows coverage from 2°- 52°. In Long-Throw Mode, using patented xR7TM technology, its provides ultra-tight beams from 0.7°-2°, incredibly without any intensity loss usually found when engaging an iris.
